at was included in the earlier lawsuit that the pornography statute applies only to publishing companies. The association has campaigned for years against the sale of magazines such as Penthouse and Playboy. The association, which has also backed boycotts of TV programs it considers offensive, most recently persuaded Matchbox to cancel sale of a <PERSON> Freddy </PERSON> <PERSON> Krueger </PERSON> doll, based on the ghoulish killer in `` Nightmare on Elm Street'' movies.
